org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.robotplus.hardware

Class TankDrive

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.robotplus.hardware.Drivetrain
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.robotplus.hardware.TankDrive
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EncoderValues

    public class TankDrive
extends Drivetrain
implements EncoderValues
    A class representing a classing TankDrive drivetrain, where there are four motors, with two on each side. No funny trickery with wheels or anything, this is the simple, "basic" drivetrain.
    Since:
    4/11/2017
